data.description: An extraordinary opportunity awaits you! Your very own piece of paradise in this beautiful secure community. This impeccably maintained 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom villa residence, complete with an additional room that can be used as an office, and a spacious 2-car garage.  Upon entry, you will discover an inviting open floor plan with features such as a formal dining area, a convenient breakfast bar, and tasteful lighting in the living, dining, and kitchen spaces. This unique unit,  includes a social membership that can be readily upgraded to a golf membership. You can explore a wealth of community insights and captivating imagery on the Hunters Ridge Golf and Country Club website
